	* Source/NSView.m: ([setNeedsDisplayInRect:]) change to ensure that
	superviews are always marked as needing display when we are.
	* Source/NSPopUpButton.m: ([-encodeWithCoder:]) ([-initWithCoder:])
	implemented for Gorm.
	
