Mon Jan 17  6:32:00 1999  Richard Frith-Macdonald <richard@brainstorm.co.uk>

	* Source/NSBundleAdditions.m: Catch exceptions when loading nib so
	we simply return YES or NO.  Fix suggested by karl@nfox.com

